lead_paragraph: Russell Westbrook had 21 points, 15 assists and 13 rebounds to help the Thunder beat the Houston Rockets 111-107 on Tuesday night.

headline.main: Westbrook's Triple-Double Leads Thunder Past Rockets 111-107
